lared an independent agencyin the s the state insurance program funded by the state and administered through the group insurance division of the department of finance was established the next decade this program was transferred to the retirement office establishing what would become today’s pehp health  benefitstoday urs and pehp provide a vast array of employee benefits urs manages a pension fund worth nearly  billion as of dec   and serves more than  members we administer members’ retirement savings plans worth a total of more than  billion pehp insures more than  individuals offering medical dental life ltd and flexible spending accountswith about  employees and under the direction of the urs board we continue to serve members in a partnership of trust with a commitment to value innovation and excellencelearn more about urs and pehpread moreread morewe are…accountantsactuariesadministrative professionalsanalystscustomer service representativesdoctorsemployer liaisonsinvestments professionalsit professionalslawyersnursesoperations specialistspharmacistspharmacy techniciansretirement advisors with  employees in health insurance and retirement savings and pension we have a position for almost everyone with plenty of progression opportunities within the organization you have the freedom to explore new opportunities read morewe serve those who serve utah our members come from a diverse range of utah’s public employers such as state of utah public and charter school systems fire districts police departments hogle zoo heber railroad mosquito abatement districts and many moreread moreutah retirement systems reviewsutah retirement systemsstarstarstarstarstarrating trendsrating trendsrecommend to a friendapprove of ceodan andersen ratings jun  urs is a great place to workstarstarstarstarstarworklife balanceculture  valuescareer opportunitiescomp  benefitssenior managementcurrent employee  anonymous employeecurrent employee  anonymous employeerecommendspositive outlookappro